Saltash]]\n*[[Tregony (UK Parliament constituency)|Tregony]]\n*[[Truro (UK Parliament constituency)|Truro]]\n*[[Truro and St Austell (UK Parliament constituency)|Truro and St Austell]]\n*[[West Looe (UK Parliament constituency)|West Looe]]\n\n===Constitutional status of Cornwall===\n* [[Revived Cornish Stannary Parliament]]\n* [[Cornwall (territorial duchy)|Cornwall]]\n* [[Duchy of Cornwall]]\n* [[Duke of Cornwall]]\n* [[Royal Commission on the Constitution (United Kingdom)|Royal Commission on the Constitution]]\n* [[Constitutional status of Cornwall]]\n* [[Stannary Courts and Parliaments]]\n* [[Cornwall Commonwealth Games Association]]\n* [[Cornish self-government movement]]\n* [[Mebyon Kernow]]\n* [[Celtic League (political organisation)|Celtic League]]\n* [[Cornish Assembly]]\n* [[Cornish Nationalist Party]]\n* [[Fry an Spyrys]]\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.cornwall.gov.uk Cornwall County Council]\n*[http://www.cornishstannaryparliament.co.uk/  The Cornish Stannary Parliament]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20070807115712/http://www.mebyonkernow.org/Public/Stories/251-1.shtml Mebyon Kernow]\n* [http://www.thisiscornwall.co.uk/displayNode.jsp?nodeId=144694&command=displayContent&sourceNode=144660&contentPK=17928446&folderPk=83364&pNodeId=144659 Tories to appoint Cornwall Minister]{{dead link|date=March 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20150205182630/http://www.kernowtgg.co.uk/ ''TGG (''Tyr Gwyr Gweryn'')'']\n*[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nIAarTqZsaU YouTube \u2013 Mark Prisk]\n\n{{Cornwall}}\n{{Celtic nations}}\n{{British political parties}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2013}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Politics Of Cornwall}}\n[[Category:Politics of Cornwall|*]]\n[[Category:Cornish nationalism]]\n", "name_user": "Iridescent", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eCornish nationalist and/or regionalist organisations:Cleanup andtypo fixing,typo(s) fixed: constituancy \u2192 